      • convertScaleToSlider

        public static int convertScaleToSlider(double scale)
        Converts a scale value to a slider value.
        Parameters:
        scale - The current scale value to be converted into corresponding slider value. The "scale" in the "scale = b^x" equation; returns the "x".
        Returns:
        The corresponding slider value.

      • convertSliderValueToScale

        public static double convertSliderValueToScale(int sliderValue)
        Converts the value on the scale slider to an appropriate integer to scale the gViewMap.
        Parameters:
        sliderValue - The slider value. The "x" in the "scale = b^x" equation; returns the "scale".
        Returns:
        The corresponding scale value.

      • loadImage

        public static java.awt.image.BufferedImage loadImage(java.lang.String path)
        Loads a buffered image from the location specified.
        Parameters:
        path - The location of the image. Expected to NOT start with a slash.
        Returns:
        The loaded buffered image.
